sequenceDiagram
    actor Customer
    participant Home as HomeView
    participant Login as LoginView
    participant API as Auth API
    participant Auth as AuthService
    participant Storage as AppStorage
    participant Tab as LiveTabView
    participant Socket as Session room
    participant Admin as Admin dashboard

    Customer->>Home: Tap Sign In
    Home->>Login: Present sheet
    Customer->>Login: Submit email + OTP
    Login->>API: POST /api/auth/login
    API-->>Login: user + mock token
    Login->>Auth: set currentUser + isAuthenticated
    Auth->>Storage: persist token and user fields
    Auth-->>Home: authenticated state
    Customer->>Tab: Open Live Tab
    Tab->>API: POST /api/session/start
    Tab->>Socket: subscribe to session_[id]
    Admin->>API: Separate unauthenticated proxy requests
    Note over API,Admin: Prototype boundary. Customer auth is mocked and admin access stays on a separate server surface.
